        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>A grinding, theatrical death-hymn: enemies within 30 feet are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.TBSHQspnbcqxsmjL]{Frightened 1} (no save, but a creature that ends its turn out of earshot recovers). His showman's counterpart, <em>Inspire Courage</em>, grants his mob +1 status to attacks, damage, and saves vs. fear.</p>"
