        },
        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Pilts targets one creature within 60 feet with a maddening harangue: @Check[type:will|dc:29] or the creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused} for 1 round (3 rounds on a critical failure; he favors <em>charm</em> and <em>hold person</em> variants — Will save, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.6uEgoh53GbXuHpTF]{Paralyzed} 1 round — as the mood takes him).</p>"
