        "category": "offensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Pilts teleports up to 120 feet — his exit, twice. Below ~20 HP he doors to his chambers (C11), spends rounds snatching favourite prizes, then doors again to vanish into Old Dock and plot revenge. Out of doors and below ~10 HP, he drops to his knees and begs, offering anything.</p>"
